{"id": "pos018", "name": "Audio_Noah_702_09_09", "res": null, "contents": [[{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["MUTE"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "......\n"}, {"id": 2, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "<font size=\"1.6\">I'm... her sister. I'm her sister...!</font>\n"}, {"id": 3, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "<font size=\"1.6\">... (Breaths deeply)</font>\n"}, {"id": 4, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Knock_Door", "Door Knock"], "content": ""}, {"id": 5, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "Aroma, good morning. Wake up!\n"}, {"id": 6, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "... Are you still asleep? You need to do a morning check up with Noah. You can sleep after we get back from that, ok? Breakfast is also ready.\n"}, {"id": 7, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "......\n"}, {"id": 8, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "... Aroma? ... Why is the door locked again!?\n"}, {"id": 9, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "<font size=\"1.6\">... 0420...</font>\n"}, {"id": 10, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Xenon's_Door_Open", "Door Opens"], "content": ""}, {"id": 11, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[»»» Fast Forward 10 minutes »»»]</i>\n"}, {"id": 12, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "... The window is open. There are footprints on the grass but they are unable to be tracked. The bent grass has dewdrops on them, which means that she has been gone for a while now. On top of that, no other traces are found.\nAroma... left here by herself.\n"}, {"id": 13, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "Noah! Look...!\n"}, {"id": 14, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "... The stabilizers... did she take them off...?\n"}, {"id": 15, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "Ah... AHHHHHHH! What should we do!? What should we do now!?\n"}, {"id": 16, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "Calm down first! There must be some clues. We need to find her as soon as possible...\n"}, {"id": 17, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "R, right! Tuner-san! Tuner-san will definitely have a record!\n"}, {"id": 18, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "She took Tuner-san with her, and she didn't answer my calls. She even went as far as turning off the location services. This means...\n"}, {"id": 19, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "She doesn't want us to find her... Noah... could it be... that she's...\n"}, {"id": 20, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Crash_Obj_01", "Things crashing"], "content": ""}, {"id": 21, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "Helena! Get a hold of yourself!\n"}, {"id": 22, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "It's my... it's all my fault. Last night, I shouldn't have said that... She must've heard us arguing... It's all because, I said those things...\n"}, {"id": 23, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "Helena... blaming yourself won't change anything. This was a decision we made back then. Therefore, we will face it together.\n"}, {"id": 24, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "...... You're right. I'm sorry, Noah. <i>*Sobs*</i>...\n"}, {"id": 25, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "Alright, stop crying... There are still plenty of things we must do.\nExcluding the option of informing the admins first, regarding the situation at Mono, how do you plan to handle it?\n"}, {"id": 26, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "We can't just hide this incident, but Mono wouldn't want to make this out to be a big deal either. The best scenario is we find Aroma ourselves. I'll report this to some of the higher-ups so they can deploy some of Mono's manpower to help the search... I'll also try my best to keep this information between just a few people.\n"}, {"id": 27, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "Understood. You go do that.\n"}, {"id": 28, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "What about you?\n"}, {"id": 29, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "I'll look around here and see if there are any clues I missed.\n"}, {"id": 30, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "Okay. I'll trust you with that, Noah...\n"}, {"id": 31, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "No problem. I'll handle this. Now go.\n"}, {"id": 32, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Xenon's_Door_Close", "Door Closes"], "content": ""}, {"id": 33, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "......\n"}, {"id": 34, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "Ahhhh... AHHHHH......\n"}, {"id": 35, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["MetalImpact", "Punches table"], "content": ""}, {"id": 36, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "<font size=\"1.6\">I... can't repent my crimes like this, can't it...? All I did was bring even more suffering... I'm sorry...</font>\n"}, {"id": 37, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[Signal Lost]</i>\n"}], [{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["MUTE"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "………\n"}, {"id": 2, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "<font size=\"1.6\">私は……お姉ちゃん。お姉ちゃん……！</font>\n"}, {"id": 3, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "<font size=\"1.6\">……スゥー…ハァー……</font>\n"}, {"id": 4, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Knock_Door", "ノック"], "content": ""}, {"id": 5, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "Aroma、おはよう！朝よ！\n"}, {"id": 6, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "……まだ寝てるの？\nNoahが朝の検査をするって。\n検査が終わってからまた寝てもいいから。\n朝ごはんの準備もできてるわよ。\n"}, {"id": 7, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "………\n"}, {"id": 8, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "……Aroma？……また鍵がかかってるわ！\n"}, {"id": 9, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "<font size=\"1.6\">……0420……</font>\n"}, {"id": 10, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Xenon's_Door_Open", "ドアが開く"], "content": ""}, {"id": 11, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[»»»10分早送り»»»]</i>\n"}, {"id": 12, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "……窓が開いてる。草の上に足跡も残ってる。\nでも追跡ができない。\n踏みつぶされた草には露が付いてる。\nつまり、Aromaちゃんがいなくなってから、時間が経過してることになるね。\n他には何の痕跡も残ってない。\nつまり、Aromaちゃんは自ら……ここを去ったんだ。\n"}, {"id": 13, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "Noah！見て……！\n"}, {"id": 14, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "……安定器……取ったのか……？\n"}, {"id": 15, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "うっ……ぅう…ああああ！\nどうしよう！？どうしたらいいの！？\n"}, {"id": 16, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "落ち着いて！\n絶対に手掛かりはあるはずだ。\n早く探さないと……\n"}, {"id": 17, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "そ、そうよ！チューナー君は！？チューナー君に何か残されてるはず！\n"}, {"id": 18, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "チューナー君のことは連れて行ったみたいだ。\n電話にも出ない。\nGPS機能も切ってしまったらしい。これは……\n"}, {"id": 19, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "私たちに見つかりたくないということ……Noah……あの子、もしかして……\n"}, {"id": 20, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Crash_Obj_01", "物がぶつかる"], "content": ""}, {"id": 21, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "Helena！しっかり！\n"}, {"id": 22, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "私が……私のせいよ。\n昨日、あんなこと言うべきじゃなかった……\n私たちがケンカしてるところを見たんだわ……\n私のせい……私があんなこと言ったから……\n"}, {"id": 23, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "Helena……自分を責めても仕方ないよ。\nこれは、僕たちがあの時決めたことだろう？\n一緒に向き合っていかないと。\n"}, {"id": 24, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "……そうね。ごめんなさい、Noah……ぅうう……\n"}, {"id": 25, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "ほら、泣かないで……\nやらなきゃならないことは、たくさんある。\n管理局には通報せずに、まずはMONOに連絡しよう。\nどうするつもりだい？\n"}, {"id": 26, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "この件は隠し通せないわ。\nでもMONOも大ごとにはしたくないはず。\n一番いいのは、私たちが自分の力でAromaを見つけ出すことだけど……\n上層部の人間に報告するわ。\nMONOのスタッフで捜索する……でも、あまり多くの人に知られるわけにはいかないわ。\n"}, {"id": 27, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "分かった。そうしよう。\n"}, {"id": 28, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "あなたは？\n"}, {"id": 29, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "何か他の手掛かりが残されてないか、ここら辺をもう少し見てみるよ。\n"}, {"id": 30, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "分かったわ。よろしくね、Noah……\n"}, {"id": 31, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "任せて。ほら、早く行って。\n"}, {"id": 32, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Xenon's_Door_Close", "ドアが閉まる"], "content": ""}, {"id": 33, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "………\n"}, {"id": 34, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "<font size=\"1.6\">ああ……ああああ……</font>\n"}, {"id": 35, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["MetalImpact", "机を叩く"], "content": ""}, {"id": 36, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "<font size=\"1.6\">僕には……こうやって罪を償うこともできないのか……？\n悪い結果しかもたらすことができない……すまない……</font>\n"}, {"id": 37, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[電波切断]</i>\n"}], [{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["MUTE"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 2, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "<font size=\"1.6\">我是……姊姊，我是姊姊……！</font>\n"}, {"id": 3, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "<font size=\"1.6\">……（深呼吸）</font>\n"}, {"id": 4, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Knock_Door", "敲門"], "content": ""}, {"id": 5, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "Aroma，早安，起床囉！\n"}, {"id": 6, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "……還在睡嗎？Noah 那邊有些晨間檢查要做，等等再回來睡好不好？早餐也準備好囉。\n"}, {"id": 7, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 8, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "……Aroma？……門怎麼又鎖了！？\n"}, {"id": 9, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "<font size=\"1.6\">……0420……</font>\n"}, {"id": 10, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Xenon's_Door_Open", "開門"], "content": ""}, {"id": 11, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[»»»快轉 10 分鐘»»»]</i>\n"}, {"id": 12, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "……窗戶是開著的，草地上留有足跡，但無法追蹤；折彎的草上結有露珠，代表她走了一段時間；而且，找不到其他痕跡。\nAroma……是自己離開的。\n"}, {"id": 13, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "Noah！你看……！\n"}, {"id": 14, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "……穩壓器……拿掉了嗎……？\n"}, {"id": 15, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "嗚嗚……嗚啊啊啊啊！怎麼辦！？怎麼辦呀！？\n"}, {"id": 16, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "妳先冷靜一點！一定有什麼線索，我們得快點找到她……\n"}, {"id": 17, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "對、對了，喇叭君！喇叭君一定會有紀錄！\n"}, {"id": 18, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "她把喇叭君帶走了，而且沒有接我的電話，甚至連定位系統都關掉了，這代表……\n"}, {"id": 19, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "她不想讓我們找到……Noah……她是不是……\n"}, {"id": 20, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Crash_Obj_01", "物品碰撞"], "content": ""}, {"id": 21, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "Helena！振作點！\n"}, {"id": 22, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "是我……是我害的，昨晚，我不該講那句話……她一定聽見我們倆在吵架了……都怪我，說了那些……\n"}, {"id": 23, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "Helena……責怪自己無濟於事，這是我們當時決定的事，要一起面對。\n"}, {"id": 24, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "……你說的對，對不起，Noah。嗚嗚……\n"}, {"id": 25, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "好了，別哭了……我們還有許多事要做。\n不考慮通報管理局，首先單聲那邊，妳打算怎麼處理？\n"}, {"id": 26, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "這件事沒辦法隱瞞，但單聲也不會想把事情鬧大，最好的情況就是我們自己把 Aroma 給找回來。我會和一些大頭報告，動用單聲的人力來搜尋……也儘量不要讓太多人知情。\n"}, {"id": 27, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "好，就這麼辦。\n"}, {"id": 28, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "那你呢？\n"}, {"id": 29, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "我在這裡看看，有沒有什麼漏掉的線索。\n"}, {"id": 30, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "好，靠你了，Noah……\n"}, {"id": 31, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "沒問題，交給我。快去吧。\n"}, {"id": 32, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Xenon's_Door_Close", "關門"], "content": ""}, {"id": 33, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 34, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "<font size=\"1.6\">啊啊……啊啊啊……</font>\n"}, {"id": 35, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["MetalImpact", "敲桌"], "content": ""}, {"id": 36, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "<font size=\"1.6\">我果然……無法靠這樣贖罪嗎……？只會帶來更多惡果而已……對不起……</font>\n"}, {"id": 37, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[訊號中斷]</i>\n"}], [{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["MUTE"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "……\n"}, {"id": 2, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "<font size=\"1.6\">나는..... 언니다…… 나는....언니다……나는.....！</font>\n"}, {"id": 3, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "<font size=\"1.6\">……（심호흡）</font>\n"}, {"id": 4, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Knock_Door", "노크"], "content": ""}, {"id": 5, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "Aroma, 좋은 아침! 어서 일어나렴!\n"}, {"id": 6, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "……아직 자고 있니? Noah가 아침에 검사해야 할 게 있다고 했으니깐 그것만 검사하고 돌아와서 다시 자도록 해. 아침밥도 이미 다 차려놨어.\n"}, {"id": 7, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "……\n"}, {"id": 8, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "……Aroma?……문을 또 잠갔어!?\n"}, {"id": 9, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "<font size=\"1.6\">……0420……</font>\n"}, {"id": 10, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Xenon's_Door_Open", "문이 열린다"], "content": ""}, {"id": 11, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[»»»10분 앞으로 빨리 감기»»»]</i>\n"}, {"id": 12, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "……창문은 열려있고 땅 위에는 발자국이 남아있지만 쫓기에는 이미 늦었어. 휘어진 풀 위에 이슬이 맺혀 있어. 이미 가버린 지 한참이나 지났다는 얘기야. 그리고 다른 흔적은 찾을 수 없었어.\nAroma는…… 스스로 떠난 거야.\n"}, {"id": 13, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "Noah! 이것은……！\n"}, {"id": 14, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "……안정 장치…… 떼어버린 건가……？\n"}, {"id": 15, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "흐흑……흐아아아앙! 어떡해 이제!? 어떡하냐고!?\n"}, {"id": 16, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "우선 진정해! 분명 단서가 있을 거야. 우린 빨리 그 아이를 찾아야 내야 해....\n"}, {"id": 17, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "그래!  맞아! 튜너 군! 튜너 군에게 분명 어떤 기록이 남겨져 있을 거야!\n"}, {"id": 18, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "튜너 군도 데리고 가버렸어. 내 전화도 받지 않고... 위치 추적 장치까지 전부 꺼버렸어... 이건...\n"}, {"id": 19, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "우리들이 찾지 않았으면 좋겠다는 말이야? ……Noah…… 그 아이 설마...\n"}, {"id": 20, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Crash_Obj_01", "물건들이 부딪힌다"], "content": ""}, {"id": 21, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "Helena! 기운 차려야지!\n"}, {"id": 22, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "나 때문이야…… 내가 그렇게 만든 거야. 어젯밤에, 그런 말을 해서는 안됐어... 분명 어제 우리 둘이 싸우는 이야기를 들었을 거야...\n"}, {"id": 23, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "Helena…… 책임을 스스로에게 돌려도 이 일은 해결되지 않아. 이건 우리들이 함께 결정했던 일이니, 해결할 때도 함께 해야만 해.\n"}, {"id": 24, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "……맞는 말이야. 미안해, Noah. 흐흐흑…\n"}, {"id": 25, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "울지 마… 우린 아직 해야 할 일이 많잖아. 관리국에 신고하는 일보다도 모노 쪽 일은 어떻게 처리할 생각이야?\n"}, {"id": 26, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "이 사건은 숨길 방법이 없어. 하지만 모노도 일을 크게 만들고 싶어 하진 않을 거야. 가장 좋은 건 우리가 Aroma를 다시 데리고 돌아오는 건데... 윗 사람들 몇 명에게만 이 사실을 알리고 사내 직원들 중 몇 명을 Aroma를 찾는데 협력해달라고 요청해볼게... 그래도 최대한 많은 사람들이 이 일을 알지 못하도록 하는 것이 좋을 것 같아.\n"}, {"id": 27, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "알았어. 그럼 그렇게 하도록 해.\n"}, {"id": 28, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "너는?\n"}, {"id": 29, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "난 이곳을 찾아볼게. 떨어뜨린 단서가 있을 수도 있으니깐...\n"}, {"id": 30, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "응. 믿고 있을게, Noah……\n"}, {"id": 31, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "응. 맡겨만 둬. 어서 가봐.\n"}, {"id": 32, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Xenon's_Door_Close", "문이 열린다"], "content": ""}, {"id": 33, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "……\n"}, {"id": 34, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "<font size=\"1.6\">크흐흑……크흑……</font>\n"}, {"id": 35, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["MetalImpact", "책상을 두드린다"], "content": ""}, {"id": 36, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "<font size=\"1.6\">역시 난…… 이런 식으로 밖에 속죄할 수 없는 걸까……? 오히려 나쁜 결과만 가지고 왔을 뿐이야…… 미안해……</font>\n"}, {"id": 37, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[신호 중단]</i>\n"}], [{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["MUTE"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 2, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "<font size=\"1.6\">我是……姊姊，我是姊姊……！</font>\n"}, {"id": 3, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "<font size=\"1.6\">……（深呼吸）</font>\n"}, {"id": 4, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Knock_Door", "敲門"], "content": ""}, {"id": 5, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "Aroma，早安，起床囉！\n"}, {"id": 6, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "……還在睡嗎？Noah 那邊有些晨間檢查要做，等等再回來睡好不好？早餐也準備好囉。\n"}, {"id": 7, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 8, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "……Aroma？……門怎麼又鎖了！？\n"}, {"id": 9, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "<font size=\"1.6\">……0420……</font>\n"}, {"id": 10, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Xenon's_Door_Open", "開門"], "content": ""}, {"id": 11, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[»»»快轉 10 分鐘»»»]</i>\n"}, {"id": 12, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "……窗戶是開著的，草地上留有足跡，但無法追蹤；折彎的草上結有露珠，代表她走了一段時間；而且，找不到其他痕跡。\nAroma……是自己離開的。\n"}, {"id": 13, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "Noah！你看……！\n"}, {"id": 14, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "……穩壓器……拿掉了嗎……？\n"}, {"id": 15, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "嗚嗚……嗚啊啊啊啊！怎麼辦！？怎麼辦呀！？\n"}, {"id": 16, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "妳先冷靜一點！一定有什麼線索，我們得快點找到她……\n"}, {"id": 17, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "對、對了，喇叭君！喇叭君一定會有紀錄！\n"}, {"id": 18, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "她把喇叭君帶走了，而且沒有接我的電話，甚至連定位系統都關掉了，這代表……\n"}, {"id": 19, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "她不想讓我們找到……Noah……她是不是……\n"}, {"id": 20, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Crash_Obj_01", "物品碰撞"], "content": ""}, {"id": 21, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "Helena！振作點！\n"}, {"id": 22, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "是我……是我害的，昨晚，我不該講那句話……她一定聽見我們倆在吵架了……都怪我，說了那些……\n"}, {"id": 23, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "Helena……責怪自己無濟於事，這是我們當時決定的事，要一起面對。\n"}, {"id": 24, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "……你說的對，對不起，Noah。嗚嗚……\n"}, {"id": 25, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "好了，別哭了……我們還有許多事要做。\n不考慮通報管理局，首先單聲那邊，妳打算怎麼處理？\n"}, {"id": 26, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "這件事沒辦法隱瞞，但單聲也不會想把事情鬧大，最好的情況就是我們自己把 Aroma 給找回來。我會和一些大頭報告，動用單聲的人力來搜尋……也儘量不要讓太多人知情。\n"}, {"id": 27, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "好，就這麼辦。\n"}, {"id": 28, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "那你呢？\n"}, {"id": 29, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "我在這裡看看，有沒有什麼漏掉的線索。\n"}, {"id": 30, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "好，靠你了，Noah……\n"}, {"id": 31, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "沒問題，交給我。快去吧。\n"}, {"id": 32, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Xenon's_Door_Close", "關門"], "content": ""}, {"id": 33, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 34, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "<font size=\"1.6\">啊啊……啊啊啊……</font>\n"}, {"id": 35, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["MetalImpact", "敲桌"], "content": ""}, {"id": 36, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "<font size=\"1.6\">我果然……無法靠這樣贖罪嗎……？只會帶來更多惡果而已……對不起……</font>\n"}, {"id": 37, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[訊號中斷]</i>\n"}], [{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["MUTE"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 2, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "<font size=\"1.6\">我是……姊姊，我是姊姊……！ </font>\n"}, {"id": 3, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "<font size=\"1.6\">……（深呼吸）</font>\n"}, {"id": 4, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Knock_Door", "敲门"], "content": ""}, {"id": 5, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "Aroma，早安，起床啰！\n"}, {"id": 6, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "……还在睡吗？ Noah 那边有些晨间检查要做，等等再回来睡好不好？早餐也准备好啰。\n"}, {"id": 7, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 8, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "……Aroma？ ……门怎么又锁了！ ？\n"}, {"id": 9, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "<font size=\"1.6\">……0420……</font>\n"}, {"id": 10, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Xenon's_Door_Open", "开门"], "content": ""}, {"id": 11, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[»»»快转 10 分钟»»»]</i>\n"}, {"id": 12, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "……窗户是开着的，草地上留有足迹，但无法追踪；折弯的草上结有露珠，代表她走了一段时间；而且，找不到其他痕迹。\nAroma……是自己离开的。\n"}, {"id": 13, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "Noah！你看……！\n"}, {"id": 14, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "……稳压器……拿掉了吗……？\n"}, {"id": 15, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "呜呜……呜啊啊啊啊！怎么办！ ？怎么办呀！ ？\n"}, {"id": 16, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "妳先冷静一点！一定有什么线索，我们得快点找到她……\n"}, {"id": 17, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "对、对了，喇叭君！喇叭君一定会有纪录！\n"}, {"id": 18, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "她把喇叭君带走了，而且没有接我的电话，甚至连定位系统都关掉了，这代表……\n"}, {"id": 19, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "她不想让我们找到……Noah……她是不是……\n"}, {"id": 20, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Crash_Obj_01", "物品碰撞"], "content": ""}, {"id": 21, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "Helena！振作点！\n"}, {"id": 22, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "是我……是我害的，昨晚，我不该讲那句话……她一定听见我们俩在吵架了……都怪我，说了那些……\n"}, {"id": 23, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "Helena……责怪自己无济于事，这是我们当时决定的事，要一起面对。\n"}, {"id": 24, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "……你说的对，对不起，Noah。呜呜……\n"}, {"id": 25, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "好了，别哭了……我们还有许多事要做。\n不考虑通报管理局，首先单声那边，妳打算怎么处理？\n"}, {"id": 26, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "这件事没办法隐瞒，但单声也不会想把事情闹大，最好的情况就是我们自己把 Aroma 给找回来。我会和一些大头报告，动用单声的人力来搜寻……也尽量不要让太多人知情。\n"}, {"id": 27, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "好，就这么办。\n"}, {"id": 28, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "那你呢？\n"}, {"id": 29, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "我在这里看看，有没有什么漏掉的线索。\n"}, {"id": 30, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "好，靠你了，Noah……\n"}, {"id": 31, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "没问题，交给我。快去吧。\n"}, {"id": 32, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Xenon's_Door_Close", "关门"], "content": ""}, {"id": 33, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 34, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "<font size=\"1.6\">啊啊……啊啊啊……</font>\n"}, {"id": 35, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["MetalImpact", "敲桌"], "content": ""}, {"id": 36, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "<font size=\"1.6\">我果然……无法靠这样赎罪吗……？只会带来更多恶果而已……对不起……</font>\n"}, {"id": 37, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[讯号中断]</i>\n"}]]}